      "role": "user",
      "content": "but i really dont have time to go to a clinic right now with work being so busy. the lubricating drops are super easy to get at the supermarket downstairs and they dont require a prescription. if i just use those for a few days, it'll probably just settle down, right? it's probably not that serious if it's just from the screen glare.",
